{"tid":2011620,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"【玩家叫苦】受「小粉紅」舉報　PSN 中國地區暫時下架","createTime":"2020-05-11T06:26:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T15:28:29.000Z","uid":295585,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2dfcdb1ffb8b02a18b6d1d3c77633375246f15fe","tid":2011620,"uid":295585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:26:57.000Z","msg":"中國大陸地區用戶因為國家的政策，所有遊戲都會經過嚴格的審查，確定沒有「色情、暴力、敏感內容」才會開放給國民購買，亦有網絡限制，用戶不能翻牆到其它網絡地區。不過只要外國地區有一些「潛在攻擊中國人」的言論或內容，都會有「愛國小粉紅」的網民翻牆攻擊，或舉報涉嫌違反中國網絡使用守則的事項，近日中國地區的 PlayStation 官方，亦因為「愛國小粉紅」的舉報而需要「更新」，導致大量中國大錄用戶不滿。<br />\n有愛國小粉紅中國網友名為「森里螢四」，檢舉Sony PlayStation 的「SIE」服務「PlayStation Network」（PSN）中國國行版，聲稱服務存有漏洞，可以讓國內的用戶，連線到包括香港地區的未經審核商店，購買並下載遊戲，可以下載《鐵血戰士》《GTA V》等「鼓吹暴力色情、血腥、販賣毒品等，嚴重危害廣大青少年身心健康的遊戲作品。」而的確成功讓 PSN 自中國下架。<br />\n中國地區的 PlayStation 表示，中國商店暫停服務通知，由於 PlayStation 中國商店系統安全升級的原因，中國地區商店將於5月10日早上七時起暫停服務，對於用戶造成的不便我們深感抱歉。<br />\n此舉導致到大量中國地區玩家指責舉報事件的愛國小粉紅，表示：「你母親節幹這種事會失去媽的」，大量玩家檢舉那位小粉紅，最後導致該名「森里螢四」網友舉報成為無效帳戶，但一切已經太遲。<br />\n<br />\n小粉紅而家連ps4都冇得玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0p26UDs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0p26UDs.jpg&h=82cd2c58&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8ptxQbO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8ptxQbO.jpg&h=c0960ff6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hE6vBRO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhE6vBRO.jpg&h=914d6207&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1S8Bxp9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1S8Bxp9.jpg&h=c499e49e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7f0303783dad44039618da1e5f9658b9be91f73c","tid":2011620,"uid":295585,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:27:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2020/05/10/psn-chian-area-block-in-may-10/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2020%2F05%2F10%2Fpsn-chian-area-block-in-may-10%2F&d=jhMTXyFjUfd7nN31cC%2BnyWqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=b2ab184a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2020/05/10/psn-chian-area-block-in-may-10/</a>"},{"pid":"f43380968f67b7672afad389bcfd58dec182c1c0","tid":2011620,"uid":160551,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T07:35:13.000Z","msg":"Fifa 一堆白金卡 果d<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1507a700ad56da61b1bc4cbb107aa3e7eb1d890","tid":2011620,"uid":128741,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T08:16:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做得好"},{"pid":"e01c6718d949890a0b8a4d0fa83b8d270a8d130d","tid":2011620,"uid":39360,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T15:28:29.000Z","msg":"新消息<br />\n巨硬驚到即時封左xbox個後門唔畀人跨服<br />\n仲有內部消息話會轉玩法<br />\n將重心擺香港，然後改為港澳陸聯保<br />\n即係大陸照賣鎖區機做樣畀官睇<br />\n但香港澳門唔鎖區既正常機喺大陸都有保養<br />\n迫d支那仔搶行版機<br />\n即係帳面巨硬大陸區蝕<br />\n但靠引支那仔買港機喺呢邊賺返"}]}